%% Data Flow Diagram - Data Science Pipelines Tekton
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Client
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant OAuthProxy as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant UI as ds-pipeline-ui<br/>3000/TCP HTTP
    participant API as ds-pipeline API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP<br/>8887/TCP gRPC
    participant MySQL as MySQL/MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP
    participant MinIO as MinIO/S3<br/>9000/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Tekton as Tekton Controller
    participant PA as Persistence Agent
    participant SWF as ScheduledWorkflow Controller
    participant MW as metadata-writer
    participant Envoy as metadata-envoy<br/>9090/TCP gRPC
    participant MLMD as metadata-grpc-server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant Cache as cache-server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,Cache: Flow 1: Pipeline Execution
    User->>Route: POST /apis/v1beta1/runs<br/>Auth: OAuth
    Route->>OAuthProxy: TLS Reencrypt
    OAuthProxy->>UI: HTTP/3000
    UI->>API: POST /apis/v1beta1/runs<br/>HTTP/8888
    API->>MySQL: Store pipeline metadata<br/>MySQL/3306 (Username/Password)
    API->>MinIO: Store pipeline artifacts<br/>HTTP/9000 (AccessKey/SecretKey)
    API->>K8sAPI: Create PipelineRun CR<br/>HTTPS/443 (SA Token)
    K8sAPI->>Tekton: Reconcile PipelineRun
    Tekton-->>K8sAPI: Update PipelineRun status

    Note over PA,API: Persistence Agent syncs status
    PA->>K8sAPI: Watch PipelineRuns/TaskRuns<br/>HTTPS/443 (SA Token)
    K8sAPI-->>PA: PipelineRun status updates
    PA->>API: Report status<br/>HTTP/8888

    Note over User,SWF: Flow 2: Scheduled Workflow
    User->>API: POST /apis/v1beta1/jobs<br/>Auth: Token Review
    API->>K8sAPI: Create ScheduledWorkflow CR<br/>HTTPS/443 (SA Token)
    SWF->>K8sAPI: Watch ScheduledWorkflows<br/>HTTPS/443 (SA Token)
    K8sAPI-->>SWF: ScheduledWorkflow event
    SWF->>K8sAPI: Create PipelineRun (on schedule)<br/>HTTPS/443 (SA Token)

    Note over MW,MySQL: Flow 3: ML Metadata Recording
    MW->>K8sAPI: Watch PipelineRuns/TaskRuns<br/>HTTPS/443 (SA Token)
    K8sAPI-->>MW: Execution events
    MW->>Envoy: Write metadata<br/>gRPC/9090
    Envoy->>MLMD: Forward<br/>gRPC/8080
    MLMD->>MySQL: Store metadata<br/>MySQL/3306 (Username/Password)

    Note over K8sAPI,Cache: Flow 4: Task Caching
    K8sAPI->>Cache: Pod admission webhook<br/>HTTPS/443 (K8s webhook auth)
    Cache->>MySQL: Check cache hit<br/>MySQL/3306 (Username/Password)
    Cache-->>K8sAPI: Mutated pod spec (if cache hit)
